## Drive Description

National Technical Research Organisation(NTRO) is a premier technical research organization of the Govt. of India, which is inter alia involved in design, development, acquisition and integration of cutting-edge technologies, in multiple domains, for generating actionable intelligence, to meet Tech-Int. requirements for the security of the nation.  
We work in domain areas such as Artificial Intelligence, Cloud Computing, Crypto logy, Communications, Cyber Security, Data Analytics, Remote sensing, Software Development, Linguistics, Maritime, Aviation,et al and have challenging real life problem statements to be addressed.  
NTRO offers internships for post graduate students pursuing M. Tech./M.E./M.Sc. for a duration of 03 to 06 months. The internship offers an attractive monthly stipend of Rs. 40,000/-(for Post graduate students).  

